      "message": "This is the same fix as in Apache MINA SSHD 3.0.0-M1. Of course details of where that remaining data is handled are different since there the proxy protocol is a filter in a proper filter chain, whereas the way it was in JGit is much less clean. The Apache MINA SSHD code is at\n\n* HTTP CONNECT: [HttpProxyConnector](https://github.com/apache/mina-sshd/blob/dev_3.0/sshd-core/src/main/java/org/apache/sshd/client/session/proxy/HttpProxyConnector.java#L148)\n* SOCKS: [Socks5ProxyConnector](https://github.com/apache/mina-sshd/blob/dev_3.0/sshd-core/src/main/java/org/apache/sshd/client/session/proxy/Socks5ProxyConnector.java#L378)\n* Handling the remaining data: [ClientProxyFilter](https://github.com/apache/mina-sshd/blob/dev_3.0/sshd-core/src/main/java/org/apache/sshd/client/session/filter/ClientProxyFilter.java#L114)",
